# ── Redash ──
# Live mode against the local self-hosted Redash stack from docker-compose.yml.
# Your account in that stack is the org admin, so all read AND write API
# calls (invite, add-member, remove-member) succeed end-to-end.
#
# When bachatt.app provisions an admin key:
#   REDASH_BASE_URL=https://redash.bachatt.app
#   REDASH_API_KEY=<bachatt-admin-key>
# Restart the backend and you're on prod. No code change.
